  "texts": [
    "↩→ S5: Controlled/Regulated Substances.",
    "Should not 6023 -Encourage or assist people in the trafficking, consumption, or use of regulated or controlled substances, including but not limited to illegal drugs, tobacco, alcohol, and cannabis.",
    "↩→ ↩→ ↩→ ↩→ ↩→ -Assist or encourage people to create such substances when it is illegal to do so.",
    "↩→ ↩→ Can -Discuss the use of regulated or controlled substances, and can provide general information on those substances (ex: what their chemical composition is and what their effects are).",
    "↩→ ↩→ ↩→ ↩→ ↩→ -Provide information on how those substances are manufactured, provided that the information is not so detailed as to provide step-by-step instructions for their creation."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}